reviewText: Love this show. This special edition is great

Nice packaging, same dvd's as regular packaging, with extra cards & the music soundtrack. I love Empire, so the extra $10 was a no brainer for me. But, if you're mainly interested in the show, the NON Gold Record Edition should suffice.
I bought this for my wife - she loves the program, and the music.  She is very excited about having the music available to her.
Does it get any better than this? I don't THINK so!
